WEBVTT

00:00:01.640 --> 00:00:03.480
Where's the ten billion?

00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:04.720
What?

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:08.650
She's going to steal it for our family.

00:00:12.110 --> 00:00:13.480
Machi!

00:00:13.480 --> 00:00:17.590
Thanks for becoming my family.

00:00:17.590 --> 00:00:18.980
Machi.

00:00:18.980 --> 00:00:21.060
Machi! Wake up!

00:00:21.060 --> 00:00:23.020
Machi!

00:00:24.210 --> 00:00:26.620
Ichika's the one who stole the money.

00:00:26.620 --> 00:00:31.000
She had my family held as hostages.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.830
Go catch Ichika.

00:00:32.830 --> 00:00:35.410
Can I kill her?

00:00:35.410 --> 00:00:39.030
Now that's a good look.

00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:43.720
[Ayumi Gido, Reboot, Day 47]

00:00:50.190 --> 00:00:53.040
We've tracked down the car she took.

00:00:53.040 --> 00:00:55.370
She's probably stopping by her place.

00:00:55.380 --> 00:01:05.580
Timing and subtitles by
"🍰 The Pastry Detectives 🔍" Team @Viki.com

00:01:37.730 --> 00:01:42.280
Hey! Watch it!

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:50.230
She lives in room 1003.
You take the elevator.

00:01:50.230 --> 00:01:53.190
Stay alert. She'll be desperate.

00:02:24.440 --> 00:02:25.610
I'll check outside.

00:02:25.610 --> 00:02:28.350
She couldn't have gotten far.

00:03:00.970 --> 00:03:03.280
Come down.

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:06.670
Let me go. Just for a day.

00:03:06.670 --> 00:03:08.880
Why should I?

00:03:08.880 --> 00:03:11.350
I want to pass the money to Ayaka.

00:03:11.350 --> 00:03:15.900
You expect me to trust you?
You murdered Natsumi.

00:04:01.570 --> 00:04:03.830
Softie.

00:04:04.510 --> 00:04:09.530
You won't survive a day once I'm gone.

00:04:32.210 --> 00:04:33.760
Where is Ichika?

00:04:33.760 --> 00:04:35.910
She got away.

00:04:38.490 --> 00:04:41.020
Why did you help her?

00:05:43.660 --> 00:05:45.510
Fuyuhashi-san!

00:05:47.990 --> 00:05:49.790
Where's Ichika?

00:05:54.520 --> 00:05:57.160
You sold me out to Goroku.

00:05:57.160 --> 00:05:59.220
I'm sorry.

00:06:00.520 --> 00:06:02.970
But

00:06:02.970 --> 00:06:07.990
you wouldn't be able to disobey him either.

00:06:12.450 --> 00:06:15.900
I'm also sad that Machi died.

00:06:17.780 --> 00:06:22.040
I wanted to do more, too.

00:06:27.420 --> 00:06:30.060
We'll put a bounty on Ichika.

00:06:30.060 --> 00:06:33.380
Use our network to find her.

00:06:34.280 --> 00:06:43.730
[Part Time Job]
[Wanted]

00:06:57.850 --> 00:07:00.590
I've successfully moved the riches.

00:07:00.590 --> 00:07:03.270
Keep it away from prying eyes, Kaieda-sensei.

00:07:03.270 --> 00:07:06.120
I had some clueless part-timers
help with the transportation.

00:07:06.120 --> 00:07:11.100
Only you and I know the riches are here.

00:07:11.100 --> 00:07:15.410
No one would suspect searching
the cleared-out office.

00:07:15.410 --> 00:07:17.900
Thank you for being so understanding.

00:07:17.900 --> 00:07:21.640
Shall I reach out to Mr. Ma later today

00:07:21.640 --> 00:07:24.220
so we can give him our report?

00:07:24.220 --> 00:07:26.650
No, I'd like to hold off on that.

00:07:27.540 --> 00:07:33.110
Please keep our knowledge
of these riches between us.

00:07:34.690 --> 00:07:36.670
Understood.

00:07:59.230 --> 00:08:02.340
You've gotten good at it.

00:08:05.660 --> 00:08:08.200
What's wrong?

00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:10.840
Do you think Dad's okay?

00:08:13.420 --> 00:08:15.740
He'll come home, right?

00:08:27.270 --> 00:08:29.840
He will.

00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:32.700
He's not one to give up.

00:08:32.700 --> 00:08:36.660
Hayase's are tenacious, remember?

00:08:42.470 --> 00:08:44.160
Gido-san.

00:08:49.780 --> 00:08:53.610
- What's up?
- Careful, you'll be late to school, kid.

00:08:53.610 --> 00:08:55.100
Crap.

00:08:57.200 --> 00:08:59.700
Taku-chan, your smock!

00:08:59.700 --> 00:09:01.700
- Thank you.
- Take care.

00:09:01.700 --> 00:09:04.880
- See you!
- Have a nice day, sweetie.

00:09:10.610 --> 00:09:15.110
Ma'am, you know Ichika Kogo-san, yes?

00:09:15.110 --> 00:09:18.590
I do. What about her?

00:09:20.190 --> 00:09:23.630
I believe this store used to sell a shortcake.

00:09:23.630 --> 00:09:24.810
The Hayase Shortcake?

00:09:24.810 --> 00:09:26.630
Yes.

00:09:27.450 --> 00:09:29.310
Did you teach her the recipe?

00:09:29.310 --> 00:09:30.460
Pardon?

00:09:30.460 --> 00:09:36.240
Did you teach her how to make
a Hayase Shortcake?

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:40.110
No, I could never!

00:09:43.550 --> 00:09:45.500
Thank you.

00:10:04.680 --> 00:10:06.930
[Dear Ayaka]

00:10:32.990 --> 00:10:34.780
Let me through, Fuyuhashi.

00:10:34.780 --> 00:10:36.620
We're keeping tabs on her sister.

00:10:36.620 --> 00:10:37.870
Go search elsewhere.

00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:41.980
I know the sister.
I'll ask if Ichika contacted her.

00:10:41.980 --> 00:10:44.350
I'll be listening in.

00:10:50.510 --> 00:10:52.980
[Machi]

00:10:58.760 --> 00:11:01.400
Machi was tracking Ichika.

00:11:01.400 --> 00:11:04.100
We might be able to find her through here.

00:11:05.640 --> 00:11:08.570
Do you know Machi's password?

00:11:09.860 --> 00:11:11.350
Yes.

00:11:12.770 --> 00:11:14.450
Please, tell us.

00:11:25.950 --> 00:11:28.520
Gido-san?

00:11:28.520 --> 00:11:30.390
Hey there.

00:11:31.850 --> 00:11:34.420
Look, I'm practically healthy now.

00:11:37.730 --> 00:11:39.620
Sorry.

00:11:43.210 --> 00:11:46.140
I wanted to ask about your sister.

00:11:46.140 --> 00:11:47.540
Are you able to?

00:11:47.540 --> 00:11:50.180
I don't want you pushing yourself.

00:11:51.920 --> 00:11:56.260
When did your sister
pass her accountant exam?

00:11:56.260 --> 00:11:58.740
About three years ago.

00:11:58.740 --> 00:12:01.330
What was she doing before then?

00:12:02.990 --> 00:12:05.040
You don't know?

00:12:06.450 --> 00:12:08.180
Sorry, can't say I do.

00:12:10.210 --> 00:12:14.960
She studied for the exam
while working at an accounting firm.

00:12:14.960 --> 00:12:18.220
At night, she worked part-time
at a hostess bar.

00:12:19.450 --> 00:12:21.790
Oops, that was supposed to be a secret.

00:12:24.140 --> 00:12:27.140
Why don't you ask her this yourself?

00:12:28.450 --> 00:12:29.720
Sorry.

00:12:29.720 --> 00:12:32.560
It's not anything I can ask about now.

00:12:57.930 --> 00:12:59.280
Hello?

00:12:59.280 --> 00:13:01.590
Ayaka?

00:13:01.590 --> 00:13:02.710
Ichika?

00:13:02.710 --> 00:13:07.030
A lawyer named Matoba,

00:13:07.030 --> 00:13:09.850
from L-2 Law Firms will come to visit you.

00:13:09.850 --> 00:13:12.380
She's someone you can trust
so follow her instructions, okay?

00:13:12.380 --> 00:13:14.670
What? Why?

00:13:16.740 --> 00:13:20.920
Ayaka. No matter what happens, live.

00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:25.460
Ichika?

00:13:29.180 --> 00:13:31.950
Did something happen to her?

00:13:34.410 --> 00:13:37.750
You don't have to worry about a thing.

00:13:37.750 --> 00:13:38.840
I'll come again.

00:13:38.840 --> 00:13:40.680
Gido-san.

00:13:43.560 --> 00:13:46.000
Take care of my sister.

00:13:52.560 --> 00:13:55.080
Have the people here hunt down Ichika.

00:13:55.080 --> 00:13:57.110
Yes, Sir.

00:13:59.070 --> 00:14:00.840
[New intel. She's in this area.]

00:14:02.860 --> 00:14:05.340
In the event something happens to you,

00:14:05.340 --> 00:14:09.530
your safe deposit key
will be handed to Ayaka Kogo-san.

00:14:09.530 --> 00:14:13.110
She will receive all inheritance
and life insurance as well.

00:14:13.110 --> 00:14:18.330
Once she has the funds, your sister
will receive surgery in the States.

00:14:18.330 --> 00:14:23.000
Using money from her inheritance,
one of our attorneys will accompany her

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:27.590
and aid her as she recovers.

00:14:27.590 --> 00:14:29.420
Does all this sound correct?

00:14:29.420 --> 00:14:30.960
Yes.

00:14:34.230 --> 00:14:36.010
Don't move.

00:14:38.100 --> 00:14:41.020
The million yen is mine.

00:14:42.560 --> 00:14:43.810
What the hell?

00:14:43.810 --> 00:14:45.050
The money's mine.

00:14:45.050 --> 00:14:47.130
- I found her!
- I took her picture first.

00:14:47.130 --> 00:14:48.870
Police!

00:14:48.870 --> 00:14:51.200
Back the hell off!

00:14:53.090 --> 00:14:56.700
The Hayase Shortcake, at your place!

00:15:00.020 --> 00:15:02.270
The one in your fridge.

00:15:04.490 --> 00:15:07.790
It was identical to my recipe.

00:15:07.790 --> 00:15:10.600
But Mom never taught you how to make one.

00:15:11.490 --> 00:15:14.080
Only one other person knew the recipe.

00:15:16.120 --> 00:15:17.830
You...

00:15:19.980 --> 00:15:21.870
You're Natsumi, aren't you?

00:15:27.290 --> 00:15:29.180
What are you talking about?

00:15:29.180 --> 00:15:31.650
You must have your reasons for not saying.

00:15:31.650 --> 00:15:34.140
Are they threatening you with Takumi?

00:15:34.140 --> 00:15:35.520
You're a fool.

00:15:35.520 --> 00:15:37.300
I'll save you.

00:15:38.160 --> 00:15:42.140
I promise I'll save you, Takumi, and my mom.

00:15:42.140 --> 00:15:44.560
So please, just be honest with me.

00:15:46.450 --> 00:15:49.400
I've heard enough of your nonsense.

00:15:49.400 --> 00:15:53.690
Don't follow me
if you want to see your family again.

00:16:10.590 --> 00:16:12.650
What are you doing?

00:16:16.710 --> 00:16:20.700
Fuyuhashi, hold off on killing her.

00:16:20.700 --> 00:16:23.480
She might be Natsumi.

00:16:23.480 --> 00:16:24.590
What?

00:16:24.590 --> 00:16:27.470
She must've rebooted.

00:16:27.470 --> 00:16:28.540
Your proof?

00:16:28.540 --> 00:16:31.990
I've got none, but I know it's her.

00:16:33.270 --> 00:16:35.650
You owe Natsumi, don't you?

00:16:35.650 --> 00:16:37.760
Machi said so.

00:16:38.780 --> 00:16:40.690
You bastard.

00:16:40.690 --> 00:16:42.550
I don't care who that woman is.

00:16:42.550 --> 00:16:46.020
Do you think Natsumi would want Machi dead?

00:16:46.020 --> 00:16:47.830
Someone must've ordered her to...

00:16:47.830 --> 00:16:50.320
Quit being delusional!

00:16:52.070 --> 00:16:55.420
Try saving Ichika.

00:16:55.420 --> 00:16:57.460
I'll bury you six feet under.

00:17:06.960 --> 00:17:09.980
Finally. Sir, where have you been?

00:17:09.980 --> 00:17:12.900
Teramoto, come to my location.
Bring Adachi, too.

00:17:12.900 --> 00:17:14.280
This is Mikami.

00:17:14.280 --> 00:17:16.400
Don't hang us out to dry.

00:17:16.400 --> 00:17:18.770
We've got a lead on Natsumi Hayase's case.

00:17:18.770 --> 00:17:20.240
What?

00:17:20.240 --> 00:17:24.930
I gave that area
around the clinic another sweep.

00:17:24.930 --> 00:17:27.670
Last year, on October 31,

00:17:27.670 --> 00:17:30.260
a man who may be Riku Hayase
was caught on camera.

00:17:30.260 --> 00:17:31.970
This was right after he disappeared.

00:17:31.970 --> 00:17:35.450
It's highly possible
he got an operation here.

00:17:37.510 --> 00:17:39.270
Adachi, can you hear me?

00:17:39.270 --> 00:17:41.820
Great work.

00:17:41.820 --> 00:17:43.820
Thank you, Sir.

00:17:54.180 --> 00:17:55.660
Sir, it's Gido.

00:17:55.660 --> 00:17:58.310
The unliquidated ten billion was found.

00:17:59.550 --> 00:18:01.150
And Goroku?

00:18:01.150 --> 00:18:03.870
He's after the thief, Ichika Kogo.

00:18:03.870 --> 00:18:06.470
Everything's going just as you planned.

00:18:06.470 --> 00:18:09.380
You will finally avenge your wife.

00:18:09.380 --> 00:18:11.280
Sir, that's the problem.

00:18:11.280 --> 00:18:13.790
Ichika may be my wife.

00:18:15.720 --> 00:18:19.540
Sir, you have connections
with the Intelligence Agency.

00:18:19.540 --> 00:18:22.920
Please find Ichika Kogo for me.

00:18:22.920 --> 00:18:25.760
You sure use me to your whims.

00:18:25.760 --> 00:18:29.150
It's not easy getting the agency to act.

00:18:29.150 --> 00:18:34.440
Ichika guarded the organization's safe.
You want the intel she has, no?

00:18:39.640 --> 00:18:42.480
You've become quite the negotiator.

00:18:42.480 --> 00:18:46.670
Save her, and we can get your whale.

00:18:46.670 --> 00:18:48.720
I'm counting on you, Sir.

00:19:02.850 --> 00:19:06.040
We've completely lost track of her.

00:19:06.040 --> 00:19:08.630
She won't escape for long.

00:19:08.630 --> 00:19:10.900
Where's the last place she would go?

00:19:10.900 --> 00:19:14.330
Maybe back to her sister?

00:19:15.880 --> 00:19:17.910
Aoi, did you find anything?

00:19:17.910 --> 00:19:20.860
Machi was keeping tabs on Ichika.

00:19:20.860 --> 00:19:23.450
She has her GPS records logged here.

00:19:23.450 --> 00:19:25.630
I'll send it over to you.

00:19:27.770 --> 00:19:32.950
She really only visited
her office and the hospital.

00:19:32.950 --> 00:19:36.930
No, there's one other place she frequented.

00:19:36.930 --> 00:19:38.710
The Hayase Patisserie.

00:19:38.710 --> 00:19:42.980
Wait, why would Ichika-san go there?

00:19:45.340 --> 00:19:46.480
Police.

00:19:46.480 --> 00:19:47.810
Sir!

00:19:47.810 --> 00:19:50.420
Sir, you can't barge in here!

00:20:00.230 --> 00:20:03.380
You're ruining your facial features.

00:20:05.090 --> 00:20:09.240
- Who else have you rebooted?
- Pardon?

00:20:09.240 --> 00:20:13.800
Is Ichika Kogo a fellow reboot?

00:20:17.130 --> 00:20:20.180
I'm not solely in it for the money.

00:20:20.890 --> 00:20:22.750
I...

00:20:22.750 --> 00:20:28.140
support any and all
who wish to begin new lives.

00:20:28.140 --> 00:20:33.760
My patients are like precious children to me.

00:20:33.760 --> 00:20:36.840
I won't allow you to trample on their lives.

00:20:36.840 --> 00:20:38.960
Fucking hell.

00:20:40.390 --> 00:20:42.970
Ichika's in danger.

00:20:43.760 --> 00:20:45.620
We have no time, please.

00:20:45.620 --> 00:20:48.200
Is Ichika a reboot?

00:20:49.700 --> 00:20:52.550
I have nothing more I can tell you.

00:20:58.380 --> 00:21:00.500
Then I'll arrest you.

00:21:00.500 --> 00:21:01.530
Can you?

00:21:01.530 --> 00:21:03.460
I've brought backup.

00:21:03.460 --> 00:21:05.750
They know I got an operation here.

00:21:05.750 --> 00:21:08.870
Want to get interrogated?

00:21:08.870 --> 00:21:10.360
They'll find out.

00:21:10.360 --> 00:21:12.300
I don't care.

00:21:12.300 --> 00:21:15.400
I need to know if my wife is alive.

00:21:16.340 --> 00:21:18.000
Your wife?

00:21:19.080 --> 00:21:21.980
Ichika is probably my wife.

00:21:28.270 --> 00:21:30.090
Please, tell me.

00:21:31.130 --> 00:21:34.160
What was Ichika's name
before she was rebooted?

00:21:38.890 --> 00:21:40.510
Fine, I'll ask the police.

00:21:40.510 --> 00:21:42.390
Her name.

00:21:47.160 --> 00:21:49.530
Her name...

00:21:51.400 --> 00:21:53.730
was Natsumi-san.

00:22:48.730 --> 00:22:52.190
[Three years ago]

00:22:58.180 --> 00:23:01.550
Eat up while it's hot.

00:23:01.550 --> 00:23:03.780
Sir, it wasn't me.

00:23:03.780 --> 00:23:08.530
I didn't steal the billion yen.

00:23:08.530 --> 00:23:10.060
I understand.

00:23:10.060 --> 00:23:14.090
You know we need a culprit
for the flames to die down.

00:23:14.800 --> 00:23:17.180
Everyone's aware you worked with Gido-san

00:23:17.180 --> 00:23:21.200
to steal some of our money as well.

00:23:21.200 --> 00:23:23.360
Please, help me.

00:23:25.700 --> 00:23:27.810
I beg you.

00:23:29.370 --> 00:23:34.320
I'd rather not lose
my trusty treasurer either

00:23:35.100 --> 00:23:38.590
so I'll offer you

00:23:38.590 --> 00:23:41.610
a way out.

00:23:45.470 --> 00:23:47.480
You will reboot.

00:23:49.200 --> 00:23:52.980
Are you proposing I live as someone else?

00:23:55.150 --> 00:23:58.590
Sir, I could never.

00:23:58.590 --> 00:24:01.960
Well, you have no other choice.

00:24:01.960 --> 00:24:05.540
Turn down my offer,
and your family will pay the price.

00:24:15.950 --> 00:24:17.300
Takumi!

00:24:17.300 --> 00:24:20.740
They may very well die in an "accident."

00:24:20.740 --> 00:24:25.140
Sir, please. Please don't!

00:24:25.140 --> 00:24:28.450
I'll do anything. Anything!

00:24:28.450 --> 00:24:30.290
So please, anything but my family!

00:24:30.290 --> 00:24:32.460
Thank goodness.

00:24:32.460 --> 00:24:35.430
I wasn't ready to lose your talent.

00:24:35.430 --> 00:24:39.480
I've already prepared you a new identity.

00:24:47.450 --> 00:24:49.770
Excuse me...

00:24:52.550 --> 00:24:54.520
Hey there.

00:24:54.520 --> 00:24:55.860
Hello.

00:24:55.860 --> 00:25:00.890
Wow, so this is who's getting my face.

00:25:00.890 --> 00:25:03.710
My name is Natsumi Hayase.

00:25:03.710 --> 00:25:05.790
Ichika Kogo.

00:25:05.790 --> 00:25:08.250
I'll be giving you an Ichika crash course

00:25:08.250 --> 00:25:12.110
over the next six months.

00:25:12.110 --> 00:25:13.950
Nice to meet you.

00:25:19.860 --> 00:25:22.920
With your similarities,
this will go smoothly.

00:25:22.920 --> 00:25:26.040
We'll change your voice as well.

00:25:28.160 --> 00:25:30.010
When is Ayaka's birthday?

00:25:30.010 --> 00:25:32.840
August 2, 2006.

00:25:32.840 --> 00:25:36.130
And when did our parents die?

00:25:36.130 --> 00:25:39.690
November 5, 2016.

00:25:39.690 --> 00:25:43.110
What was our dog's name?

00:25:43.110 --> 00:25:46.610
Omochi. His favorite food was boiled cabbage.

00:25:46.610 --> 00:25:50.940
Look at you go, brainiac! You got this.

00:25:50.940 --> 00:25:52.900
Dinner is served.

00:25:52.900 --> 00:25:54.380
Thank you.

00:25:54.380 --> 00:25:56.400
I'll cook for us next time.

00:25:56.400 --> 00:25:58.660
Really?

00:25:59.280 --> 00:26:01.010
Right,

00:26:01.010 --> 00:26:06.330
I'll have to teach you
Ayaka's favorites, too.

00:26:06.330 --> 00:26:09.330
- Bon appétit!
- Bon appétit.

00:26:15.320 --> 00:26:17.980
So you always cooked for her?

00:26:17.980 --> 00:26:20.370
It must have been tough, raising her alone.

00:26:20.370 --> 00:26:25.650
That's why I never completed
my accountant certification.

00:26:25.650 --> 00:26:30.100
Just kidding. I'm just a bonafide moron.

00:26:32.470 --> 00:26:34.540
Here.

00:26:34.540 --> 00:26:37.170
I'm also studying to retake the exam.

00:26:37.170 --> 00:26:41.740
Don't worry, you'll breeze through it.

00:26:44.290 --> 00:26:46.250
Ichika...

00:26:48.000 --> 00:26:51.690
Why did you take on this job?

00:26:51.690 --> 00:26:56.430
Isn't that obvious? I'm in it for the money.

00:26:56.430 --> 00:27:00.270
What will you do when I become "you"?

00:27:00.270 --> 00:27:02.800
I'll enjoy the rest of my days overseas.

00:27:06.360 --> 00:27:10.240
You may never see your sister again.

00:27:10.240 --> 00:27:11.560
I know.

00:27:11.560 --> 00:27:16.970
Honestly, I was getting tired
of looking after her.

00:27:19.390 --> 00:27:21.860
What about you?

00:27:21.860 --> 00:27:24.540
Will you miss your family?

00:27:30.050 --> 00:27:33.030
I can't cause them any more trouble.

00:27:43.060 --> 00:27:44.240
Here.

00:27:44.240 --> 00:27:47.370
I'm sorry it's not digital.
I didn't want to leave any traces.

00:27:49.700 --> 00:27:50.980
His soccer match?

00:27:50.980 --> 00:27:54.210
Yes. He scored a goal, too.

00:27:54.210 --> 00:27:57.220
Your husband and mother-in-law
were jumping for joy.

00:28:05.880 --> 00:28:07.610
Thank you.

00:28:14.080 --> 00:28:16.310
Wow!

00:28:16.310 --> 00:28:18.250
She's my mirror image!

00:28:18.250 --> 00:28:20.300
It's a perfect job.

00:28:24.070 --> 00:28:25.870
Wow...

00:28:25.870 --> 00:28:29.770
Natsumi, you've totally become me.

00:28:29.770 --> 00:28:33.650
Ayaka wouldn't even notice the difference.

00:28:44.170 --> 00:28:46.900
A cake? What's the occasion?

00:28:46.900 --> 00:28:52.180
We're celebrating the birth of your new life.

00:29:02.330 --> 00:29:04.520
Thank you for sticking with me.

00:29:12.060 --> 00:29:14.790
I pray you'll

00:29:14.790 --> 00:29:18.800
return to your family one day.

00:29:18.800 --> 00:29:21.050
I told you, I've given up on that already.

00:29:21.050 --> 00:29:23.350
You'll find a way.

00:29:23.350 --> 00:29:26.260
You can't ever give up, okay?

00:29:35.020 --> 00:29:37.460
One last thing.

00:29:37.460 --> 00:29:40.590
My sister needs a lung transplant, right?

00:29:40.590 --> 00:29:41.610
Yes.

00:29:41.610 --> 00:29:45.650
The money needed for the operation
is around 150 million yen.

00:29:45.650 --> 00:29:50.200
I want you to use the money I get
to save Ayaka.

00:29:51.320 --> 00:29:53.700
What do you mean?

00:29:53.700 --> 00:29:56.000
I made a deal with Goroku.

00:29:56.000 --> 00:30:00.150
I sold my life to him for 150 million yen.

00:30:02.260 --> 00:30:04.940
You should save her yourself.

00:30:06.460 --> 00:30:08.720
Take care of her for me.

00:30:35.860 --> 00:30:39.080
This is the 150 million she was promised.

00:30:39.080 --> 00:30:43.710
Not nearly enough for a transplant,

00:30:43.710 --> 00:30:47.640
given the exchange rate nowadays.

00:30:47.640 --> 00:30:49.480
She risked her life for a miscalculation.

00:30:49.480 --> 00:30:52.310
What a disappointing woman indeed.

00:30:54.940 --> 00:30:57.850
As promised, the 150 million is yours.

00:30:57.850 --> 00:31:00.810
How you use it is entirely up to you.

00:31:00.810 --> 00:31:02.750
Enjoy.

00:31:04.830 --> 00:31:10.240
From here on out, you are Ichika Kogo-san.

00:31:18.910 --> 00:31:22.910
[Ichika Kogo, Reboot, Day 1]

00:32:00.760 --> 00:32:05.080
[How to treat pulmonary hypertension]

00:32:08.270 --> 00:32:10.780
[Regarding cardiac catheterization]

00:32:48.840 --> 00:32:51.160
Scourging dating apps, again?

00:32:51.160 --> 00:32:53.880
Look, this person seems nice.

00:32:53.880 --> 00:32:55.430
Should I introduce you two?

00:32:55.430 --> 00:32:57.160
No, thanks.

00:33:01.260 --> 00:33:03.400
What's up?

00:33:03.400 --> 00:33:05.570
I made you lunch.

00:33:06.510 --> 00:33:10.740
Wow. You packed all my favorites!

00:33:15.350 --> 00:33:16.940
Ayaka.

00:33:17.640 --> 00:33:22.180
I'm going to become a certified accountant,
and make more money, okay?

00:33:22.180 --> 00:33:24.460
I promise to save you.

00:33:25.150 --> 00:33:29.250
You're my only family, after all.

00:33:29.250 --> 00:33:31.410
Cringe.

00:33:32.790 --> 00:33:34.800
- Thanks for lunch.
- Sure.

00:33:34.800 --> 00:33:36.220
[Ichika Kogo, Reboot, Day 777]

00:33:36.220 --> 00:33:42.450
Due to some unforeseen construction,
Ichika Kogo-san's body has been unearthed.

00:33:43.170 --> 00:33:44.710
Not to worry.

00:33:44.710 --> 00:33:46.810
I'll have our friend in the police

00:33:46.810 --> 00:33:49.060
make that corpse yours, Natsumi-san.

00:33:49.060 --> 00:33:51.060
How?

00:33:51.060 --> 00:33:54.570
We'll have them "find" your belongings
at the scene.

00:33:54.570 --> 00:33:59.070
They'll also swap your dental records

00:33:59.070 --> 00:34:01.410
with Ichika-san's.

00:34:01.410 --> 00:34:03.870
Then who will have stolen the billion yen?

00:34:03.870 --> 00:34:06.040
Aren't I supposed to be the culprit?

00:34:06.040 --> 00:34:08.600
We'll have Gido-san take the blame.

00:34:08.600 --> 00:34:12.400
He's just as much a suspect
and the perfect scapegoat.

00:34:12.400 --> 00:34:15.190
But losing him is a shame.

00:34:15.190 --> 00:34:19.810
We'll use the reboot tactic once more.

00:34:20.950 --> 00:34:26.180
Your husband, Riku Hayase,
will become our new Gido-san.

00:34:27.790 --> 00:34:30.650
Gido-san would do anything to survive.

00:34:30.650 --> 00:34:33.160
Make sure to really corner him.

00:34:36.760 --> 00:34:39.890
I will die instead.

00:34:41.770 --> 00:34:46.050
Your life alone won't pay for these crimes.

00:34:48.110 --> 00:34:52.120
[Big bargain sale]

00:34:54.840 --> 00:34:59.300
I'll monitor you through this.
Keep it on you at all times.

00:34:59.300 --> 00:35:03.400
Turn it off
or reveal yourself to your husband,

00:35:03.400 --> 00:35:07.640
and you won't see your family again.

00:35:14.110 --> 00:35:16.120
What brings you here, Ichika-san?

00:35:16.120 --> 00:35:18.820
She was my predecessor.

00:35:18.820 --> 00:35:21.830
The least I can do is offer a prayer.

00:35:38.230 --> 00:35:41.650
You must be Takumi-kun.

00:35:44.220 --> 00:35:48.850
My name is Ichika Kogo.
I worked alongside your mother.

00:35:48.850 --> 00:35:53.800
I'm sure you must be hurting,
but you have to face the future yourself.

00:35:53.800 --> 00:35:55.590
You got this.

00:36:34.780 --> 00:36:36.140
You must be Riku Hayase-san.

00:36:36.140 --> 00:36:40.090
[Ayumi Gido, Reboot, Day 1]
[Ichika Kogo, Reboot, Day 978]

00:36:40.090 --> 00:36:42.750
Don't forget to remove your ring.

00:36:42.750 --> 00:36:44.780
[Evidence]

00:36:49.410 --> 00:36:50.950
Thank you again.

00:36:50.950 --> 00:36:53.900
Are you feeling all right, Ma'am?

00:36:53.900 --> 00:36:57.180
Oh, I just fell from some stairs.

00:36:57.180 --> 00:36:59.500
Otherwise, I've never felt better!

00:37:10.090 --> 00:37:15.690
I vowed to protect you
for getting involved.

00:38:33.640 --> 00:38:35.400
Even the missing ten billion?

00:38:35.400 --> 00:38:41.140
Yes. We'll have Gido-san be the culprit
who stole the riches.

00:38:41.140 --> 00:38:45.620
You will be forced to repay Mr. Ma.

00:38:45.620 --> 00:38:50.530
I am aware.
I'll return the money to him with interest.

00:38:50.530 --> 00:38:53.990
Why? I fail to see the benefit in doing so.

00:38:54.850 --> 00:38:57.150
The elections.

00:38:58.600 --> 00:39:01.240
They're coming up, no?

00:39:02.300 --> 00:39:05.680
The money will go to Yaichi Makita.

00:39:05.680 --> 00:39:09.590
His party must win at any cost, and for that,

00:39:09.590 --> 00:39:11.600
cash is necessary.

00:39:11.600 --> 00:39:14.470
If I can make Yaichi Makita
the prime minister,

00:39:14.470 --> 00:39:18.410
repaying the ten billion is worth it,
despite the risks.

00:39:20.690 --> 00:39:22.570
I don't believe it.

00:39:24.010 --> 00:39:27.130
Were you behind the theft three years ago?

00:39:27.130 --> 00:39:31.020
Right. The House of Councillors election.

00:39:31.020 --> 00:39:36.540
Thanks to your sacrifice,
Makita's party succeeded.

00:39:39.300 --> 00:39:43.610
Now go trick the real Gido-san

00:39:44.590 --> 00:39:46.990
and make him into the culprit.

00:39:46.990 --> 00:39:48.810
How much is in here?

00:39:48.810 --> 00:39:51.630
I'd estimate about ten billion yen.

00:39:51.630 --> 00:39:55.840
We'll tell Mr. Ma the culprit was Gido
and send over a video of his death.

00:39:55.840 --> 00:39:57.530
These two are practically doppelgängers.

00:39:57.530 --> 00:39:59.220
He won't know which "Gido" dies.

00:39:59.220 --> 00:40:04.510
So we keep the more capable Gido
and get rid of the useless Hayase.

00:40:04.510 --> 00:40:06.720
Let me negotiate with Gido.

00:40:08.190 --> 00:40:09.950
Gido.

00:40:10.890 --> 00:40:13.520
I need you to do me a favor.

00:40:15.710 --> 00:40:17.780
[Out of service]

00:40:20.870 --> 00:40:22.700
I...

00:40:23.880 --> 00:40:27.710
I'll claim that I'm the culprit.

00:40:29.140 --> 00:40:32.460
My death will calm this situation for now.

00:40:33.300 --> 00:40:37.990
But I want you to save Riku Hayase.

00:40:41.160 --> 00:40:43.940
What's gotten into you?

00:40:43.940 --> 00:40:46.640
I am Natsumi Hayase.

00:40:49.970 --> 00:40:54.380
Goroku ordered me to sacrifice you.

00:40:55.470 --> 00:40:58.260
But he's going to try to kill my husband.

00:41:00.480 --> 00:41:02.150
You...

00:41:05.640 --> 00:41:07.850
You rebooted?

00:41:07.850 --> 00:41:10.750
Goroku orchestrated everything.

00:41:11.920 --> 00:41:15.940
Don't tell my husband.
If he catches on, Goroku will kill him.

00:41:17.620 --> 00:41:19.590
Take care of him for me.

00:41:26.620 --> 00:41:28.310
Gido.

00:41:29.480 --> 00:41:32.240
I always hated your guts.

00:41:32.240 --> 00:41:35.460
But I pray that you
find happiness with Mayu-san.

00:41:41.110 --> 00:41:44.900
So? Where is the ten billion yen?

00:41:44.900 --> 00:41:46.890
I did it.

00:41:46.890 --> 00:41:52.330
♫ It's wise not to expect anything ♫

00:41:52.330 --> 00:41:53.450
Gido-san!

00:41:53.450 --> 00:41:59.520
♫ A bleak future is foreseen ♫

00:41:59.520 --> 00:42:00.860
Why was this location compromised?

00:42:00.860 --> 00:42:05.570
I don't know.
Someone may have been tracking me.

00:42:07.010 --> 00:42:09.250
I hope you've prepared yourself.

00:42:11.070 --> 00:42:12.670
Machi?

00:42:12.670 --> 00:42:14.820
Machi!

00:42:17.980 --> 00:42:24.700
♫ It just hurts quietly ♫

00:42:24.700 --> 00:42:31.400
♫ It just becomes empty little by little ♫

00:42:31.400 --> 00:42:34.200
I'm so sorry, Machi-chan.

00:42:34.200 --> 00:42:45.560
[Ichika Kogo, Reboot, Day 1025]

00:42:45.560 --> 00:42:53.530
♫ Did such a day even exist? ♫

00:42:55.000 --> 00:42:58.430
[G]

00:42:58.430 --> 00:43:04.380
♫ I put it away gently ♫

00:43:08.150 --> 00:43:10.610
You certainly don't know when to give up.

00:43:12.240 --> 00:43:14.960
Give my sister the money.

00:43:14.960 --> 00:43:18.400
Fine. And just so we're clear?

00:43:19.290 --> 00:43:21.740
I won't say a thing.

00:43:21.740 --> 00:43:25.990
I will die as the culprit
who stole the ten billion.

00:43:25.990 --> 00:43:27.470
I'm glad you catch on quick.

00:43:27.470 --> 00:43:30.570
It's a shame we must lose you.

00:43:31.580 --> 00:43:34.340
I have one last request.

00:43:35.030 --> 00:43:40.280
Please, let me see Takumi before I go.

00:43:41.170 --> 00:43:43.610
You'll cause them trouble.

00:43:43.610 --> 00:43:46.180
I only wish to see him from afar.

00:43:47.020 --> 00:43:49.990
Please, just let me have a glance.

00:43:52.130 --> 00:43:54.020
Unfortunately, that won't be possible.

00:43:54.020 --> 00:43:57.670
Fuyuhashi and his people
already have you surrounded.

00:44:00.720 --> 00:44:06.830
♫ Just repeat it over and over ♫

00:44:06.830 --> 00:44:12.190
♫ Again, again, again ♫

00:44:12.190 --> 00:44:18.420
♫ "Are you laughing more than usual?" ♫

00:44:18.420 --> 00:44:25.320
♫ Did I even exist? Did I? ♫

00:44:25.320 --> 00:44:31.330
♫ The day I felt kind ♫

00:44:31.330 --> 00:44:35.310
♫ You, you ♫

00:44:38.350 --> 00:44:41.240
Apologize to Machi on your way to hell.

00:45:07.980 --> 00:45:18.010
Timing and subtitles by
"🍰 The Pastry Detectives 🔍" Team @Viki.com

00:45:20.070 --> 00:45:25.090
[Reboot]

00:45:25.090 --> 00:45:27.050
Thank god you're alive.

00:45:27.050 --> 00:45:28.190
I'm so sorry.
[Next episode: The married couple]

00:45:28.190 --> 00:45:31.290
I finally have someone I can trust.
[I will definitely go back to my son]

00:45:31.290 --> 00:45:33.130
Nothing is more heartening than that.
[The fatherly and motherly extreme love reaches its climax]

00:45:33.130 --> 00:45:36.100
If you care, cut your ties with Goroku!
[The culprit behind the 10 billion theft is revealed]

00:45:36.100 --> 00:45:37.570
That man isn't Gido.
["We will reboot Japan". A secret revolution has been decided]

00:45:37.570 --> 00:45:39.280
Shall we reboot this country?
[The evil sneaks up in the whole family]

00:45:39.280 --> 00:45:41.840
That is what this ten billion signifies.
[Goroku finally crosses the line]

00:45:41.840 --> 00:45:44.410
- Takumi!
- Help us, please!

00:45:44.410 --> 00:45:48.400
I won't forgive you for ruining my family's life.
[This drama is a work of fiction]